{"tid":20142,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先搭地鐵嚇到個毒撚唔敢出聲","createTime":"2016-12-03T07:50:18.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T11:02:24.000Z","uid":12980,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d55aaa92a9c9a99a595920d56b1e0cb60b6a424b","tid":20142,"uid":12980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T07:50:18.000Z","msg":"話說頭先搭地鐵 同個女同事搭緊扶手電梯落去月台 <br />\n咁我同佢都企左係同一級度捉住個扶手唔郁 <br />\n之後後面有個死毒撚無啦啦拍一拍我同我講野<br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 毒撚：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n毒撚：唔該借借<br />\n<br />\n我：(無理佢繼續同隔離個女同事吹水 ) <br />\n<br />\n毒撚：唔該可唔可以借一借<br />\n<br />\n我心諗有女同事係隔離緊係唔可以咁隨便就借啦 之後就chok 住聲咁問佢<br />\n<br />\n我：借左幾時還呀？我係唔鐘意借呀吹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後電梯都到左月台 佢急急腳都跑去上車<br />\n<br />\n我再補多句：趕住去投胎咩死毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最尾見住佢面紅耳赤 怒不敢言個樣連我個女同事都忍唔住笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a146cc4ba2ed9e98350504f9ad6c6e2e068cf3","tid":20142,"uid":8569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T07:54:32.000Z","msg":"又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be3e311972967c9571b930d2c0b6bca052788868","tid":20142,"uid":861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T07:59:31.000Z","msg":"你收皮啦 你以為我怕你呀 我偷拍左你放你上網公審<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5905c26ddddd4d2524e5259b29d6800077451337","tid":20142,"uid":14272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T08:03:04.000Z","msg":"留名等睇真心膠"},{"pid":"babb54b46c616ac6b5c7ec2fee6560843b9d9eb5","tid":20142,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T08:04:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名等睇真心膠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c5fd569b93e5ff60adffe713034879b9a310b2","tid":20142,"uid":3739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T08:09:30.000Z","msg":"頭先搭地鐵，見到電梯有一男一女企左係到，個男成隻狗咁對個女擺哂尾。我望一望個女個背影，嘩屌，隻腳粗過我條腰，我即刻忍笑，驚比個男聽到。<br />\n因為驚忍唔住笑左出黎，我拿拿聲跑上去，諗住叫個男借一借比我快d走，點知條好樣問我借左幾時還？呢個時候我再望一望條女，點解d五官d位咁奇怪?。。。我再出盡奶力忍笑。<br />\n終於，等到電梯上到去，我已經忍笑忍到塊面紅哂，即刻急急腳走算，最後仲比佢串左句毒向左走向右走冇女之類既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce7203e9358c5e1de32b3ca7328eaa7535c6791","tid":20142,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T08:12:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頭先搭地鐵，見到電梯有一男一女企左係到，個男成隻狗咁對個女擺哂尾。我望一望個女個背影，嘩屌，隻腳粗過我條腰，我即刻忍笑，驚比個男聽到。<br />\n因為驚忍唔住笑左出黎，我拿拿聲跑上去，諗住叫個男借一借比我快d走，點知條好樣問我借左幾時還？呢個時候我再望一望條女，點解d五官d位咁奇怪?。。。我再出盡奶力忍笑。<br />\n終於，等到電梯上到去，我已經忍笑忍到塊面紅哂，即刻急急腳走算，最後仲比佢串左句毒向左走向右走冇女之類既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實果隻公狗係導盲犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73fc6442f783ff383e39d7f96c502dbc3f5e5d94","tid":20142,"uid":22898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T08:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07f0a21790a19510d7129663017e6c4677fed979","tid":20142,"uid":12980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T08:15:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名等睇真心膠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真人真事 岩岩係金鐘站發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4b3cd222bf6e86ce1b0cb0d124079a3965830d","tid":20142,"uid":7215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T08:19:05.000Z"